---
title: Balsamci Farro and Brussels Sprouts with Sunflower Seeds
description: Crispy, savoury balsamic Brussels sprouts tossed with tender farro are the perfect side pairing for any meal, any night of the week! Topped with toasted sunflower seeds and cranberries for a juicy burst of colour and taste!
